source.name: Approved Permits
source.description:
Abstract
City Clerk issued permit information and locations. The dataset contains locations, if applicable, and attributes of City Clerk issued permits applied for in the City of Ann Arbor. The City Clerk permit process is described on the City of Ann Arbor website.

Point of contact

City Clerk's Office
Jacqueline Beaudry
2nd floor, City Hall
100 North Fifth Avenue
Ann Arbor, MI  48104
734.794.6140
Email: cityclerk@a2gov.org
Hours:  Monday to Friday 8am-5pm
